nodes.text: An unidentified cook worked for the Whiphid crime boss known as Lady Valarian at the time of the Galactic Civil War. After Valarian killed her husband D'Wopp in 0 BBY, the body was shipped to planet Toola in a box, with several parts missing. The cook was the only other person, with Valarian herself, to know where the missing body parts had gone.
